              <span><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pass Your Instrument Written Exam</strong> Study and solidify core instrument rating concepts.  Be able to reach approach plates and IFR charts.  Understand the United States Air Traffic Control System and your role a pilot in the system.</span>
