          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">Are you a pilot wondering if getting an instrument rating is worth it? If so, you're not alone. Many pilots ask themselves the same question, and it's a decision that requires careful consideration.  But before we get into the benefits of an instrument rating, it's important to understand exactly what are the requirements.</p>
